@o_str
@ro_str
@os_str
@ros_str

@c_str -> Configuration{Orbital}

Construct a Configuration, representing a non-relativistic configuration, out of a string.

julia> c"1s2 2s"
1s² 2s

julia> c"[Kr] 4d10 5s2 4f2"
[Kr]ᶜ 4d¹⁰ 4f² 5s²

@rc_str -> Configuration{RelativisticOrbital}

Construct a Configuration representing a relativistic configuration out of a string.

julia> rc"[Ne] 3s 3p- 3p"
[Ne]ᶜ 3s 3p⁻ 3p

julia> rc"[Ne] 3s 3p-2 3p4"
[Ne]ᶜ 3s 3p⁻² 3p⁴
